{"tid":761880,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"估唔到今日仲有人J緊世界杯外圍賽，美斯係救世主....","createTime":"2018-07-30T18:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T11:58:33.000Z","uid":43785,"like":38,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"46af3173bf94545218abae048c5fee4257385720","tid":761880,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T18:30:57.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲有人Ｊ實力，講緊美斯帶帽幫阿根廷入世界杯，美斯係救世主！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日同時睇到三個POST都有巴打講緊，我想講你地仲講黎乜鳩野？<br />\n事隔咁耐，當時美斯幾場散步受盡千夫所指，係咪想趁人唔記得反轉黎講洗人腦？<br />\n其實你地搞清楚成件事未？<br />\n<br />\n世界杯外圍賽最後關鍵四場外圍賽：<br />\n烏拉圭　　０：０<br />\n委內瑞拉　１：１<br />\n秘魯　　　０：０<br />\n厄瓜多爾　１：３　阿根廷<br />\n<br />\n場場有美斯，頭三場自己散步軟腳蟹，冇波入，和鳩晒，<br />\n面臨出局邊緣，最後一場發力入三球就話佢做救世主。<br />\n講果個咪傻架？<br />\n佢真係咁救世既，要嬴一早應該羸左委內瑞拉同秘魯。洗撚等最後一刻先黎贏咩？<br />\n<br />\n其實頭三場踢得好就唔洗等第四場啦　ＯＮ９<br />\n我想講美斯頭三場冇表現，外界屌撚到暈<br />\n入波只係將功補過，佢唔係乜野救唔救世主。<br />\n<br />\n你話美斯頭三場冇出，最後一場先出，一場入三球我就話佢係救世主。<br />\n但場場出晒散步冇波入，最後一場先入，就唔算囉。OK？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：有J美斯球會表現，但國家隊？不了！"},{"pid":"fe21e3e6d5ef361bffeb338540da35d1a98bbb9f","tid":761880,"uid":43785,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T18:35:07.000Z","msg":"佢最後關鍵出四場先贏一場。<br />\n好意思講救世主？<br />\n你前面三場散步呀！！！！！<br />\n腳軟呀！！！！<br />\n<br />\n搞到成隊陷入困境呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f2510748229e236ace2fe52292f9b0458a9ffb","tid":761880,"uid":7612,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T18:36:00.000Z","msg":"球會表現就球王 冇佢爭得遠<br />\n但國家隊冇佢都未係好大損失"},{"pid":"acf5e6375f38b73757ba24fec92a4ace77e5866a","tid":761880,"uid":43785,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T18:39:34.000Z","msg":"世界杯出到線同出唔到線，都係因為美斯。<br />\n頭三場自己軟腳蟹，冇波入，和鳩晒<br />\n最後一場發力又可以代表到乜野？<br />\n<br />\n佢係成隊核心，成件事根本上神又係佢鬼又係佢。<br />\n<br />\n踢四場羸一場＝救世主？我絕對唔認同"},{"pid":"a5bf5bce493ab2d6c756e7b12aed7f6f14d60bb9","tid":761880,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T23:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fbf3b8816d60bb25f4762113ffe9fd086651e0e","tid":761880,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"09f2510748229e236ace2fe52292f9b0458a9ffb","tid":761880,"uid":7612,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T18:36:00.000Z","msg":"球會表現就球王 冇佢爭得遠<br />\n但國家隊冇佢都未係好大損失"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T23:49:58.000Z","msg":"係，國家隊踢到舊屎咁，<br />\n我只支持巴塞美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717dd5eef6d829345270eb87d3facb1811f78261","tid":761880,"uid":163207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:06:33.000Z","msg":"鳩Sir你太嚴厲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a60f45928c3b0f19e493fa9db8b4ae29b8461e4","tid":761880,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:19:32.000Z","msg":"我認得你<br />\n你咪係反梅西大聯盟既大將"},{"pid":"f2e08b961462bec446171cc722a8efca2989af38","tid":761880,"uid":30476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:20:06.000Z","msg":"輸教練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ddfcb674794420cd002f19a71edf13e6670bb24","tid":761880,"uid":50595,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3a60f45928c3b0f19e493fa9db8b4ae29b8461e4","tid":761880,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:19:32.000Z","msg":"我認得你<br />\n你咪係反梅西大聯盟既大將"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:21:34.000Z","msg":"仲利申<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家啲朗迷低賤到要扮花迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee8160243218edc239872dcb8ccfe81ae08406e","tid":761880,"uid":171107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2